| PBT-01 | Lookup cascade always returns L2 before L1 | PBT | High | Property | BR-01, BR-02 | hypothesis installed | Seed L2+L1 with same tool; verify lookup returns l2\_cache | source=l2\_cache for all generated inputs |
| PBT-02 | Error classification is deterministic | PBT | High | Property | BR-11, BR-12 | hypothesis installed | Classify same error twice; verify same result | result1 == result2 for all inputs |
| PBT-03 | Hit count is monotonically non-decreasing | PBT | High | Property | BR-08, BR-16 | hypothesis installed | Execute N times; verify hits never decreases | hits[i] <= hits[i+1] |
| PBT-04 | Dedup title format is unique per scope+tool | PBT | High | Property | BR-10 | hypothesis installed | Same (scope,tool) same title; different different | Bijective mapping |
| PBT-05 | Injection count respects configured N | PBT | Medium | Property | BR-15, BR-21 | hypothesis installed | get\_injection returns at most N tools | len(result) <= N |
| PBT-06 | Cache entry serialization roundtrip | PBT | Medium | Property | BR-03, BR-19 | hypothesis installed | from\_kb\_content(to\_kb\_content()) roundtrip | Roundtrip equality |
| UT-01 | L2 cache hit returns tool immediately | UT | High | Functional | UC-01, BR-01, BR-02 | KB seeded with L2 entry | Seed L2; call cache\_lookup; verify source=l2\_cache | Returns ToolCacheEntry source=l2\_cache |
| UT-02 | L1 cache hit when L2 misses | UT | High | Functional | UC-01, BR-01 | KB seeded with L1 only | Seed L1 only; lookup as qa-agent; verify l1\_cache | Returns ToolCacheEntry source=l1\_cache |
